stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ProjectListed
    
    ProjectListed: Homeowner lists solar project
    ProjectListed: Target $20,000 for 1,000 shares
    
    ProjectListed --> CrowdFunding: Investors buy shares
    
    CrowdFunding: Fractional ownership via NFTs
    CrowdFunding: Progress 0% to 100%
    
    CrowdFunding --> FullyFunded: Target reached
    
    FullyFunded: Funding complete
    FullyFunded: Funds to homeowner
    FullyFunded: Installation begins
    
    FullyFunded --> Operational: Panels installed
    
    Operational: Generating electricity
    Operational: IoT sensors active
    Operational: Real-time monitoring
    
    Operational --> RevenueFlow: Energy sold to grid
    
    RevenueFlow: Automated revenue split
    RevenueFlow: 5% Maintenance Reserve
    RevenueFlow: 2% Insurance Fund
    RevenueFlow: 93% Investor Dividends
    
    RevenueFlow --> Operational: Continuous cycle
    
    Operational --> MaintenanceNeeded: Equipment needs repair
    
    MaintenanceNeeded: Issue detected
    MaintenanceNeeded: Inverter malfunction or
    MaintenanceNeeded: Panel damage or
    MaintenanceNeeded: Wiring issue
    
    MaintenanceNeeded --> ProposalCreated: Token holder submits proposal
    
    ProposalCreated: Repair proposal created
    ProposalCreated: Cost estimate provided
    ProposalCreated: Vendor selected
    ProposalCreated: Voting period starts
    
    ProposalCreated --> VotingActive: Token holders vote
    
    VotingActive: Democratic voting
    VotingActive: Weight by token ownership
    VotingActive: 7 day voting period
    VotingActive: Requires >50% approval
    
    VotingActive --> VotingEnded: Deadline reached
    
    VotingEnded --> ProposalApproved: Votes > 50%
    VotingEnded --> ProposalRejected: Votes <= 50%
    
    ProposalApproved: Repair approved
    ProposalApproved: Funds released from reserve
    ProposalApproved: Vendor receives payment
    
    ProposalApproved --> RepairInProgress: Work begins
    
    RepairInProgress: Vendor repairs equipment
    RepairInProgress: Progress tracked
    
    RepairInProgress --> RepairComplete: Work finished
    
    RepairComplete: Equipment operational
    RepairComplete: System verified
    
    RepairComplete --> Operational: Back to generating
    
    ProposalRejected: Repair denied
    ProposalRejected: Reserve funds preserved
    ProposalRejected: Can resubmit with changes
    
    ProposalRejected --> MaintenanceNeeded: Revise and resubmit
    ProposalRejected --> Operational: Issue not critical
    
    Operational --> TokenListed: Investor lists tokens for sale
    
    TokenListed: Token listed on DEX
    TokenListed: Seller sets ask price
    TokenListed: Visible to all buyers
    
    TokenListed --> TokenSold: Buyer purchases on DEX
    
    TokenSold: Ownership transferred
    TokenSold: USDC paid to seller
    TokenSold: New holder receives future dividends
    
    TokenSold --> Operational: Project continues unchanged
    
    TokenListed --> TokenDelisted: Seller cancels listing
    
    TokenDelisted: Listing removed
    TokenDelisted: Tokens returned to seller
    
    TokenDelisted --> Operational: Investor holds tokens

    Operational --> Depreciation: Annual valuation
    
    Depreciation: Asset value adjusts
    Depreciation: Year 1 = 96% original
    Depreciation: Year 5 = 80% original
    
    Depreciation --> Operational
    
    Operational --> ExitOption: Institutional buyer
    
    ExitOption: Buyout at fair value
    ExitOption: All investors paid
    ExitOption: Proportional to ownership
    
    ExitOption --> [*]
    
    note right of ProjectListed
        Platform lists available
        solar projects for funding
    end note
    
    note right of CrowdFunding
        Micro-investors buy shares
        as low as $20 each
    end note
    
    note right of RevenueFlow
        Smart contracts automatically
        distribute revenue 24/7
        
        5% builds repair reserve
    end note
    
    note right of MaintenanceNeeded
        Issues can be detected by:
        - IoT sensors
        - Performance monitoring
        - Homeowner report
        - Inspector report
    end note
    
    note right of ProposalCreated
        Any token holder can create
        
        Proposal includes:
        - Problem description
        - Cost estimate
        - Vendor quote
        - Timeline
    end note
    
    note right of VotingActive
        Democratic governance
        - No intermediaries
        - Transparent on blockchain
        - Weighted by ownership
        - Cannot vote twice
    end note
    
    note right of ProposalApproved
        Automatic execution:
        - Reserve fund decreases
        - USDC sent to vendor
        - No manual intervention
        
        All transparent on-chain
    end note
    
    note right of RepairComplete
        Verification:
        - Photos uploaded to IPFS
        - Performance metrics improve
        - Energy generation restored
    end note
    
    note right of TokenListed
        Secondary market via Uniswap
        - No lock-in period
        - Instant liquidity
        - Price set by market
        - Project operations unaffected
    end note
    
    note right of TokenSold
        Ownership transfer:
        - Smart contract updates balance
        - Seller exits investment
        - Buyer inherits dividend rights
        - No platform approval needed
    end note